        "- X~u~ = $\\frac{\\tau_{a;u}^{550}}{\\tau_{a}^{550}}$ \\[u $\\in \\{ DU,BC,OC,SE,SU\\}\\rbrack$ from MERRA-2\n",
        "\n",
