        "\n",
        "- The X~u,i~ basis for the 148 predefined models are stored in a text file and read once.\n",
        "\n",
        "So, it is possible simply to choose a couple of aerosol models that fit best with the MERRA-2 data and run SMAC-CL on an ensemble of models. We rely here on the AMIP dataset (see section 2.4) that yields an ensemble of 10 aerosols models globally monthly. An example is given in Figure 4 .\n",
