        "### Tile-Based Processing\n",
        "\n",
        "| Aspect | Description |\n",
        "|----|----|\n",
        "| What | Processes the image in overlapping tiles (`batch_size` × `batch_size` with a halo) |\n",
        "| Why | Bounded memory per tile, parallel processing across workers |\n",
