        "\n",
        "## Tile Processing Architecture\n",
        "\n",
        "The processing pipeline uses a tile-based architecture for memory-bounded, parallel execution:\n",
        "\n",
        "```         \n",
        "process_batched() -- Main entry point\n",
        " 1. Generate tile grid from input extent\n",
        "    - Tile size: chunks_size x chunks_size\n",
        "    - Overlap: +/-1 pixel halo\n",
        "    - Total tiles: ceil(y/chunks) x ceil(x/chunks)\n",
        " 2. Precompute ancillary cache (if enabled)\n",
        "    - Interpolate MERRA-2 to full grid\n",
        "    - Save to local Zarr cache\n",
        " 3. Create worker pool (nworkers)\n",
        "    - Fork workers before populating _SHARED\n",
        "    - Copy-on-write inheritance of large objects\n",
        " 4. Process tiles in parallel\n",
        "    - _worker_compute_tile() per tile\n",
        "    - SMAC-CL run (VNIR + SWIR)\n",
        "    - Uncertainty propagation\n",
        "    - Write tile to NetCDF\n",
        " 5. Move local output to final destination\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "`_worker_compute_tile()` performs the end-to-end tile computation:\n",
        "\n",
        "1.  Read tile data from the input L1C file and the ancillary cache\n",
        "2.  Interpolate the DEM and compute terrain (slope/aspect)\n",
        "3.  Select the aerosol model (closest in 5D species space)\n",
        "4.  Run SMAC-CL (VNIR bands, then SWIR band)\n",
        "5.  Compute the BRDF effect (Lambertian vs BRDF run, if enabled)\n",
        "6.  Compute the terrain effect (CESBIO model)\n",
        "7.  Compute the RTM fit uncertainty (ONNX model)\n",
        "8.  Propagate uncertainties (`compute_urtoc()`)\n",
        "9.  Build quality flags (`build_flag()`)\n",
        "10. Write the tile to the output NetCDF\n",
        "\n",
        "## Output Format Details\n",
        "\n",
        "The output NetCDF file follows CF-1.8 conventions, with attributes applied from `cf_attributes_res2.json`.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Dimensions:**\n",
        "\n",
        "| Dimension | Size     | Description                              |\n",
        "|-----------|----------|------------------------------------------|\n",
        "| `bands`   | 4        | B1 (Blue), B2 (Red), B3 (NIR), B4 (SWIR) |\n",
        "| `height`  | Variable | Tile height (y dimension)                |\n",
        "| `width`   | Variable | Tile width (x dimension)                 |\n",
        "\n",
        ": Output NetCDF dimensions\n",
        "\n",
        "**Global attributes:**\n",
        "\n",
        "| Attribute     | Description                          |\n",
        "|---------------|--------------------------------------|\n",
        "| `sensor`      | Sensor name (Proba-V, SPOT-VGT)      |\n",
        "| `date`        | Acquisition date                     |\n",
        "| `time`        | Mean acquisition time (UTC)          |\n",
        "| `projection`  | Projection attributes from input L1C |\n",
        "| `conventions` | CF-1.8                               |\n",
